channel.title: RSHighScore Searching Utility
channel.description:
I did this since I can't come up with a decent idea to start on my own projects or in real life, so enjoy I guess.
Download link: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?o5m8zs8xeps1jrq]RSHighscore.rar[/url]
[IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/1zqsi83.png[/img]
Basic usage is just typing in the name in the search bar and then pressing enter to search. Improve as you wish ")
[IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/m8juhl.png[/img]
Your first improvement to it, is proper exception handling for an invalid username searched. I could do it but I just noticed this problem as I was taking a picture. If anyone wants a rerelease with that fixed, just ask.

Also it is rather pointless to post the code of something that is so small, open source, and easy to download and view.

@T4, the virus scan is regarding that people generally feel safer if their isn’t any apparent hidden files or programs that could affect their computer. I included image files in the data folder.
